Hellen Mubanga (amụrụ na 23 Mee 1995) bụ onye Zambia na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agba ọsọ dị ka onye na-agbachitere ndị otu Segunda División Pro nke Spain Zaragoza CFF na ndị otu ụmụ nwanyị Zambia. Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị otu na afọ 2014 African Women's Championship na afo 2018 Africa Women's Cup of Nations
Na klọb, ọ na-egwuri egwu maka Red Arrows Ladies team ma bụrụbu nke Bauleni Sports Academy na Zambia.
